Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.50,0:00:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.75,0:00:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗妖精那個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.35,0:00:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼時候\N才把妮絲的餅乾拿來啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.26,0:00:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修拉姆大人\N新產品"稻蝗豆餡年糕"完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.63,0:00:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嚐嚐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.53,0:00:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.90,0:00:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太甜了!餡太甜啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.49,0:00:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餡給我重做!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.31,0:00:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當今時下的小姐們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.54,0:00:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只對減少低熱量的\N減肥食品有興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.68,0:00:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把甜味降低\N才能凸顯餡的美味啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.71,0:00:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?你問我為何對餡如此執著?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.52,0:00:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為我是餡的廚師\N餡的COOKER
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.25,0:00:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗黑的騎士啊!\N(諧音)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.22,0:00:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，不愧是阿修拉姆大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.67,0:00:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連說笑話都不輸給卡修\N真是高明啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.99,0:00:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的\N就是用超美味的點心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.93,0:01:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將羅德斯的人們的心全部擄獲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.50,0:01:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了完成"三明餡餅乾"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.92,0:01:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論如何都需要妮絲的餅乾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.77,0:01:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.92,0:01:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會用我的點心稱霸羅德斯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.15,0:01:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.75,0:01:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能走出迷宮真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.15,0:01:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然遭遇很慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.79,0:01:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看到史派克那麼有精神\N也就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.26,0:01:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還送我們餅乾帶回去當土產呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.86,0:01:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我們是為了什麼事\N才去找史派克他們的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.13,0:01:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說阿修拉姆盯上妮絲的餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.97,0:01:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以為了讓史派克\N能夠好好對付他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.84,0:01:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才千里迢迢去送這把魔法劍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是這樣啊，魔法劍嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.34,0:01:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這把劍戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.91,0:01:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要平安完成任務喔，史派克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.48,0:01:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這把劍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.72,0:01:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.55,0:01:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了給他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.65,0:01:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.85,0:01:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦，史派克?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.85,0:01:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請繼續收看緊迫盯人的下一集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.32,0:01:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
